metadata.name: 兎姫道中
metadata.description:
兎姫は月姫さまに宝物を献上しに旅にでます
途中の峠には怪盗カラス一味が出ると言われています
兎姫一行はお宝を守ることができるのでしょうか

Princess Usagi sets out on a journey to present her treasures to the Moon Princess.
It is said that a gang of ravens, the phantom thieves, will appear at the mountain pass on the way.
Will Princess Usagi and her friends be able to protect the treasure?
